---

<section id="story" class="story-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="story-inner">
      <div class="story-text">
        <h2 class="section-title reveal">The Story</h2>
        <p class="story-para reveal">
          Mr. Rich wakes up in his room. His hands are transparent. His dog is barking beside him.
        </p>
        <p class="story-para reveal">
          One question haunts him: <em>How do I find the way out?</em>
        </p>
        <p class="story-para reveal">
          Together — a ghost who cannot touch the world, and a dog who refuses to leave his side —
          they must work as one to unravel the mysteries of a house that traps them both.
        </p>
        <p class="story-para reveal">
          A puzzle game about companionship, mutual dependence, and understanding what truly matters
          before the last walk is over.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="story-silhouette reveal-right">
        <img src="/MrRich.png" alt="Mr. Rich" class="silhouette-ghost" />
        <img src="/angel.png" alt="Angel" class="silhouette-dog" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.story-section {
  padding: 8rem 0;
  background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--dark-900), var(--dark-800));
}

.story-inner {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 4rem;
  align-items: center;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .story-inner {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }
}

.story-text .section-title {
  color: var(--gold-400);
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.story-para {
  font-size: 1.15rem;
  line-height: 1.8;
  color: var(--cream-100);
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  transition-delay: 0.1s;
}

.story-para em {
  color: var(--ghost-400);
  font-style: italic;
}

.story-silhouette {
  position: relative;
  height: 320px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-end;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 2rem;
}

.silhouette-ghost {
  height: 240px;
  width: auto;
  object-fit: contain;
  animation: ghostFloat 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  filter: drop-shadow(0 0 16px rgba(94,179,179,0.4));
}

.silhouette-dog {
  height: 160px;
  width: auto;
  object-fit: contain;
  animation: dogWag 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  filter: drop-shadow(0 0 12px rgba(232,169,82,0.35));
}

@keyframes ghostFloat {
  0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
  50% { transform: translateY(-16px); }
}

@keyframes dogWag {
  0%, 100% { transform: rotate(-3deg); }
  50% { transform: rotate(3deg); }
}
</style>
